name: Puzzle for the board game SAVING PENGUIN ON THE ICE
description: The board game "SAVING PENGUIN ON THE ICE" is a fun and challenging puzzle game that will test your strategic thinking and problem-solving skills. With colorful and engaging game pieces, this game is perfect for players of all ages. Get ready to embark on an exciting adventure and save the penguin from the treacherous ice!
